      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical choice for a value-focused buyer seeking reliable transportation at an accessible price point. It shows age and wear consistent with an older pre-owned vehicle, but remains a solid opportunity for everyday use, a second car, or a project. Offered with straightforward value in mind, this is a chance to secure dependable mobility without stretching your budget.",
