      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, budget-friendly option that could make a great runaround, first project, or handy backup vehicle. It\u2019s being sold as a used car with wear consistent with age and use, and it\u2019s priced to reflect that. If you want something cheap, straightforward, and full of potential, this could be a great fit.",
